pve-manager (9.1.1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * ui: storage: oci registry pull: make parsing the reference of a OCI image
    URL more robust and add a validator to the reference field for better
    immediate feedback to the user.

  * ui: storage oci pull: reword empty text for tag field to avoid suggesting
    that this placeholder is the default value, as we currently do not have
    any here.

 -- Proxmox Support Team <support@proxmox.com>  Tue, 18 Nov 2025 19:08:54 +0100

pve-manager (9.1.0) trixie; urgency=medium

  * bump for Proxmox VE 9.1.

 -- Proxmox Support Team <support@proxmox.com>  Tue, 18 Nov 2025 00:32:05 +0100

pve-manager (9.0.18) trixie; urgency=medium

  * ui: resource tree: fix rendering of guest text when sorted by name.

  * ui: fix recent regression from wrongly rendering guest entries in the tag
    view.

